# ChineseLanguageEngage Monorepo

Monorepo for game mods that add Chinese language-learning support.

## Structure

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `cedict/` | Shared CEDICT dictionary data (runtime dependency for all mods) |
| `shadowrun-returns/mod/` | BepInEx plugin for Shadowrun Returns (Unity 4.2.0f4) |
| `shadowrun-returns/preprocessor/` | Python pipeline for Shadowrun Returns `.po` files |

## Conventions

- Game directories use kebab-case (e.g. `shadowrun-returns`, `baldurs-gate-2`).
- Each game has `mod/` (runtime plugin, own `.sln`) and `preprocessor/` (Python, depends on `pinyiniser`).
- CEDICT is shared; preprocessors are game-specific (different file formats per game).
